item.title: About me
item.author: leon@kiesgen.eu (Leon Kie)
item.description: Mechanical engineer and maker. I love to come up with unique solutions for unknown problems and this is the right space for my personal projects that what to be noticed :). What is this Blog about? I have done several projects in the past involving arduinos, mechatronics or simple mechanical designs mostly around 3d printing. However, in the future, I also want to share some more software orientated projects and creative stuff that comes into my mind.
